## 🎓 v5.8.1 설계 패턴

### 패턴 1: 값 래퍼 (Value Wrapper)

```rust
struct Sealed<T> {
    value: T,
    metadata: String,
}

impl<T> Sealed<T> {
    fn new(value: T, meta: &str) -> Self {
        Self {
            value,
            metadata: String::from(meta),
        }
    }

    fn open(&self) -> &T {
        &self.value
    }
}
```

### 패턴 2: 결과 래퍼 (Result Wrapper)

```rust
struct Operation<T> {
    result: Result<T, String>,
}

impl<T> Operation<T> {
    fn success(value: T) -> Self {
        Self { result: Ok(value) }
    }

    fn failure(error: &str) -> Self {
        Self { result: Err(String::from(error)) }
    }

    fn unwrap_or(self, default: T) -> T {
        self.result.unwrap_or(default)
    }
}
```

### 패턴 3: 컨테이너 (Container)

```rust
struct Container<T> {
    items: Vec<T>,
}

impl<T> Container<T> {
    fn new() -> Self {
        Self { items: Vec::new() }
    }

    fn push(&mut self, item: T) {
        self.items.push(item);
    }

    fn pop(&mut self) -> Option<T> {
        self.items.pop()
    }

    fn len(&self) -> usize {
        self.items.len()
    }
}
```

